{"tid":1485214,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[屌你老母]致今日金鐘留守班自私撚！","createTime":"2019-08-18T15:40:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T16:54:26.000Z","uid":12792,"like":80,"dislike":43,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"1d9e05155b650c78fa34e576d43fd8e7ca7bcd93","tid":1485214,"uid":12792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:40:34.000Z","msg":"唔想屌你地係鬼，我信你哋係真手足<br />\n但可唔可以跟返大圍意見去做<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一句不割蓆唔撚代表你可以自把自為到咁撚樣</span></span><br />\n<br />\n係tg/連登 etc 叫左你地散左4個幾鐘，係咪可以咁撚自私？！<br />\n<br />\n我哋今日晒人數，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">目的係屌鳩班差佬嘅流水式集會係幾咁戇鳩，逼佢批返正常遊行</span></span><br />\n今日和理非要贏一仗，和理非今日爬山，多謝勇武配合，大家一齊贏<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">點撚解要做啲咁撚冇意義嘅留守？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n聽日新聞又全部都係你哋啦，咁我哋今日170萬人風吹雨打，比無限把遮刮眼，做緊乜撚嘢？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n真心，唔割，但要教育下呢班人！<br />\n今日係維園浸左兩粒幾鐘，比無數嘅遮刮眼，再行左勁長路，我好撚唔甘心咁樣輸收尾！"},{"pid":"66afdfa304bb9de2c6ff632fb303a4800b3515cd","tid":1485214,"uid":293798,"like":19,"dislike":3,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:41:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"783ad608eff7c5ee8f2dfc43e4c66397603be1a1","tid":1485214,"uid":12792,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:43:19.000Z","msg":"對唔住話我分化都係咁講，點解咁低智？"},{"pid":"ce94c3e46cd2995d80388d5a58e9014b85a67d79","tid":1485214,"uid":12792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:43:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"349daa05f2eb750e76dd801517b0e07f122d3df7","tid":1485214,"uid":12792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:45:33.000Z","msg":"自推，隨便負評"},{"pid":"e6893fd2b1fa1196d68b6a701c471fa7997001a6","tid":1485214,"uid":12792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:45:49.000Z","msg":"我發洩下"},{"pid":"555916d3e94f3ff9bda2896af477fd3a11cfa747","tid":1485214,"uid":12792,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-