34e576d43fd8e7ca7bcd93","tid":1485214,"uid":12792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:40:34.000Z","msg":"唔想屌你地係鬼，我信你哋係真手足<br />\n但可唔可以跟返大圍意見去做<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一句不割蓆唔撚代表你可以自把自為到咁撚樣</span></span><br />\n<br />\n係tg/連登 etc 叫左你地散左4個幾鐘，係咪可以咁撚自私？！<br />\n<br />\n我哋今日晒人數，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">目的係屌鳩班差佬嘅流水式集會係幾咁戇鳩，逼佢批返正常遊行</span></span><br />\n今日和理非要贏一仗，和理非今日爬山，多謝勇武配合，大家一齊贏<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">點撚解要做啲咁撚冇意義嘅留守？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n聽日新聞又全部都係你哋啦，咁我哋今日170萬人風吹雨打，比無限把遮刮眼，做緊乜撚嘢？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n真心，唔割，但要教育下呢班人！<br />\n今日係維園浸左兩粒幾鐘，比無數嘅遮刮眼，再行左勁長路，我好撚唔甘心咁樣輸收尾！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:19:36.000Z","msg":"8.18 2350 同場加映黑警臥底扮完示威者 行番入狗屋收工<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/295202647488775/permalink/1764292657246426?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F295202647488775%2Fpermalink%2F1764292657246426%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=T%2BmtXVGNOTzTHFJD9Tq3cXGrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=152d596f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/295202647488775/permalink/1764292657246426?sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"b857119a1acd679ae594c821d47478ae268d1e8e","tid":1485214,"uid":12792,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"10827a7acbf83d6565362582bdab8527259bf580","tid":1485214,"uid":194601,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:16:45.000Z","msg":"其實唔走 同你前線割我地和理非席有咩分別 專重喇 不割𥱊 不分化"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:19:40.000Z","msg":"岩呀！講明和理非場，係咪唔俾和理非爬山？係咪要踐踏和理非努力？<br />\n<br />\n係咪撚少日狗會毒癮發作？"},{"pid":"7c58559667a237b4dc88f4e3e37c5ce1c240a825","tid":1485214,"uid":12792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c08a22ea052122355a3899433c2328ca348fba62","tid":1485214,"uid":226955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":